		## Solution to Installing and Configuring Ansible on Linux ##
		#############################################################

# Task 1 -
	# yum install ansible

# If working with RHEL and have subscription then :
	a)	Register machine :
		- subscription-manager register
		: Enter username & Password when prompted

	b)	Attach it to pool of Repos :
		- subscription-manager attach --pool=<POOL_ID>

	c)	Enable Repository :
		- subscription-manager repos --enable rhel-7-server-ansible-2.6-rpms

	d)	Verify installation :
		- ansible version
		
	e) 	Optinally, you can execute verify_installation.sh
